item.description:
Ukulele play along Come On Eileen - Dexy's Midnight Runners
Using the chords: A Bb C D Em F F#m G
Suggested Strum Patterns: D DU U DU ** This song really needs various strum patterns, I have suggested different ones at the bottom of the screen but there may be others you prefer.
